<item>
            <title>[FELIX-2022] [Branding] webconsole.product.image not treated correctly when referencing http resource</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-2022</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When setting webconsole.product.image or webconsole.vendor.image to a http URL for an external image the default branding plugin treats the value still as a relative path to its bundle root.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The generated HTML code looks like this&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;img src=&quot;/system/consolehttp://www.somesite.com/sites/default/files/rec_logo.png&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12447073">FELIX-2022</key>
