                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12828596" author="fmeschbe" created="Tue, 2 Feb 2010 10:59:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for reporting this issue. I have fixed it in Rev. 905574 by ensuring not to prefix any branding setting which migh be an absolute URL. Assumption is that an absolute path (leading slash) is to be prefixed and  anything else need not be prefixed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
